summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of West Sixty-seventh Street, from Eighth Avenue N. W. to Fourteenth Avenue N. W. et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 21198, creating Local Improvement District No. 2104 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
